local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["pecan"]={"pecan","['piːk(ə)n; pɪ'kæn; pɪ'kɑːn]","[pɪ'kɑn]","n.美洲山核桃（树）",'n.美洲山核桃（树）','A confection made of nut kernels, especially almonds or pecans, stirred in boiling sugar syrup until crisp and brown.','干果糖用干果仁，尤指杏仁或山核桃仁在沸腾的糖浆里搅拌直至发焦变脆而制成的蜜饯','Although pecans are most plentiful in the southeastern part of the United States, they are found as far north as Ohio and Illinois.','虽然美洲山河桃树最集中于美国的东南部但是在北至俄亥俄州及伊利诺州也能看见它们。'}
